<text top="410" left="89" width="1033" height="18" font="1">Fringe beneﬁts have been paid in cash and/or to bona ﬁde fringe beneﬁt plans, funds, or programs. Where the contractor is claiming an hourly credit for their contributions to or reasonably </text>
<text top="426" left="89" width="992" height="18" font="1">anticipated costs of a bona ﬁde fringe beneﬁt plan, fund, or program, provide plan information and the hourly credit claimed for each worker listed on the previous page of this form.</text>
<text top="426" left="1081" width="3" height="18" font="0"> </text>
